rk model during the model\ntraining; and the prediction speed is four orders faster than the CFD. The\nability of the accurate and extremely faster prediction of the network model\nsuggests the potentials of applying such kind of models to the applications of\nreal-time control, optimization, and design in future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jan 2021 03:59:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-12"}
