 Different nonlinear methods will be compared to one another and to\nthe original fixed-point implementation on a newly proposed 2-systems academic\ntest-case (mass-spring-damper type) with direct feedthrough on both sides.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jan 2021 09:42:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-13"}
